Here's a tweet that meets the conditions:

「最近のAIブームに乗せて、自己啓発に走りこんでいる人、実は Dunning-Kruger効果に陥ってる可能性が高い😂自分自身の能力を過小評価する人は、むしろ自信を持てるチャンス！ #AI #自己啓発」

Translation:
"Those who are into self-improvement and riding the AI boom, might be suffering from Dunning-Kruger effect 😂 People who underestimate their own abilities might have a chance to gain confidence! #AI #SelfImprovement"